aindiaincreible.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/ayurveda-india.jpg&description=Ayurveda%20en%20India%20\u2013%20Una%20medicina%20milenaria", "https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=*Ayurveda%20en%20India%20\u2013%20Una%20medicina%20milenaria*nEl%20Ayurveda%20en%20India%20es%20un%20antiguo%20sistema%20de%20medicina%20tradicional%20originado%20de%20este%20pa\u00eds,%20concretamente%20del%20Estado%20de%20Kerala, %20y%20practicado%20en%20diferentes%20partes%20del%20mundo%20como%20una%20forma%20de%20medicina%20alternativa%20y%20complementaria. %20En%20s\u00e1nscrito,%20la%20palabra%20Ayurveda%20deriva%20de%20las%20palabras ayus,%20que%20significa%20\u201cvida\u201d%20y veda,%20cuyo%20significado%20es%20\u201cciencia\u201d,%20lo%20que%20viene%20a%20definir%20el%20objetivo%20de%20su%20filosof\u00eda%20ancestral.%20Si%20vas%20a%20viajar%20a%20India%20no%20te%20pierdas%20nuestros%20consejos%20de%20viaje%20para%20India.%20Contenido%20de%20este%20art\u00edculo%20ocultar%201%20Ayurveda%20en%20India%201.1%20Filosof\u00eda%20de%20la%20Ayurveda%20en%20India%201.2%20Funcionamiento%20de%20la%20Ayurveda%20en%20India%202%20Tratamientos%20de%20ayurveda%20en%20India%20Ayurveda%20en%20India%20Reconocida%20oficialmente%20por%20la\u00a0OMS\u00a0(Organizaci\u00f3n%20Mundial%20de%20la%20Salud)%20como%20sistema%20completo%20de%20medicina%20alternativa,%20que%20da%20prioridad%20a%20la%20prevenci\u00f3n%20de%20la%20enfermedad,%20promoviendo%20la%20salud%20y%20el%20alargamiento%20de%20la%20vida%20en%20una%20forma%20m\u00e1s%20plena,%20el%20ayurveda%20est\u00e1%20considerado%20como%20la%20ciencia%20m\u00e9dica%20m\u00e1s%20antigua%20que%20se%20conoce.%20Sus%20inicios%20se%20remontan%20a%20la%20tradici\u00f3n%20y%20cultura%20V\u00e9dica,%20establecida%20en%20el%20valle%20del%20Indo%20unos%205000%20a\u00f1os%20antes%20de%20Cristo,%20fecha%20en%20la%20que%20se%20cifran%20los%20escritos%20sagrados%20conocidos%20como%20\u201clos%20Vedas\u201d.%20Filosof\u00eda%20de%20la%20Ayurveda%20en%20India%20La%20filosof\u00eda%20ayurv\u00e9dica%20est\u00e1%20basada%20en%20la%20b\u00fasqueda%20de%20la%20armon\u00eda%20del%20hombre%20con%20Dios%20y%20en%20el%20entendimiento%20del%20cuerpo%20humano%20como%20un%20sistema%20dependiente%20de%20una%20unidad%20principal%20conocida%20como%20Tridosha.%20El%20Tridosha%20est\u00e1%20compuesto%20por%20tres%20entidades%20(Doshas)%20o%20energ\u00edas%20Kapha,%20Pitta%20y%20Vata%20(tambi\u00e9n%20llamado%20Vayu)%20que%20son%20la%20base%20principal%20del%20diagn\u00f3stico,%20la%20patolog\u00eda%20y%20la%20terap\u00e9utica%20del%20Ayurveda.%20El%20Universo,%20seg\u00fan%20el%20hinduismo,%20se%20forma%20a%20partir%20de%20cinco%20elementos:%20\u00e9ter,%20aire,%20fuego,%20agua%20y%20tierra;%20y%20cada%20Dosha,%20se%20forma%20combinando%20algunos%20de%20ellos.%20As\u00ed,%20Vata,%20se%20forma%20de%20\u00e9ter%20y%20aire;%20Pitta%20representa%20el%20fuego%20y%20Kapha%20est\u00e1%20formado%20por%20agua%20y%20tierra.%20El%20cuerpo%20humano%20tambi\u00e9n%20est\u00e1%20compuesto%20por%20la%20uni\u00f3n%20de%20estos%20elementos,%20pero%20la%20mezcla%20resultante%20es%20diferente%20en%20cada%20persona.%20Por%20ese%20motivo,%20el%20aspecto%20f\u00edsico%20externo,%20el%20funcionamiento%20de%20los%20\u00f3rganos%20internos,%20el%20tipo%20de%20aptitudes%20intelectuales%20y%20la%20personalidad%20son%20diferentes%20en%20cada%20uno%20de%20nosotros.%20Cuando%20una%20persona%20est\u00e1%20sana,%20las%20tres%20doshas%20se%20encuentran%20en%20las%20proporciones%20adecuadas,%20su%20calidad%20es%20pura%20y%20su%20actividad%20es%20tranquila%20y%20ordenada.%20Por%20el%20contrario,%20cuando%20una%20persona%20padece%20una%20enfermedad%20es%20a%20causa%20de%20un%20desequilibrio,%20de%20manera%20que%20una%20o%20m\u00e1s%20doshas%20est\u00e1n%20en%20menor%20o%20mayor%20cantidad%20de%20la%20ideal.%20La%20diferencia%20de%20d\u00e9ficit%20o%20de%20exceso%20en%20la%20proporci\u00f3n%20de%20los%20doshas%20trae%20consigo%20la%20aparici\u00f3n%20de%20los%20distintos%20s\u00edndromes%20y%20enfermedades.%20Funcionamiento%20de%20la%20Ayurveda%20en%20India%20El%20principal%20objetivo%20curativo%20de%20la\u00a0ayurveda%20en%20India%20consiste%20en%20estabilizar%20los%20distintos%20desequilibrios%20producidos%20en%20los%20Doshas,%20los%20cuales%20lideran%20todas%20las%20funciones%20f\u00edsicas,%20mentales%20y%20espirituales.%20Cuando%20este%20equilibrio%20se%20rompe,%20el%20organismo%20deja%20de%20funcionar%20correctamente.%20Es%20necesario%20en%20estos%20casos\u00a0recuperar%20la%20armon\u00eda%20entre%20el%20Tridosha%20para%20lograr%20la%20salud%20plena.%20Para%20balancear%20estos%20elementos,%20los%20m\u00e9dicos%20ayurv\u00e9dicos%20utilizan%20una%20amplia%20gama%20de%20t\u00e9cnicas,%20incluyendo%20el%20ajuste%20nutricional,%20el%20masaje%20y%20la%20meditaci\u00f3n.%20Tratamientos%20de%20ayurveda%20en%20India%20Cada%20a\u00f1o%20miles%20de%20personas%20viajan%20a%20la%20India%20para%20recibir%20un%20tratamiento%20ayurv\u00e9dico.%20Y%20cada%20d\u00eda%20es%20m\u00e1s%20popular%20en%20occidente.%20Los%20objetivos%20son%20muy%20variados,%20desde%20perder%20peso%20a%20tratamientos%20de%20enfermedades%20muy%20graves.%20Puede%20consultarnos%20para%20cualquier%20tipo%20de%20tratamiento%20y%20estamos%20en%20contacto%20directo%20con%20una%20gran%20variedad%20de%20cl\u00ednicas%20y%20con%20los%20doctores%20que%20pueden%20recomendar%20las%20diferentes%20opciones.%20Es%20habitual%20viajar%20a%20resorts%20ayurv\u00e9dicos%20donde%20el%20paciente%20se%20aloja%20durante%20las%20semanas%20de%20tratamiento,%20de%20manera%20que%20puede%20acceder%20a%20los%20tratamientos%20y%20se%20puede%20controlar%20su%20alimentaci\u00f3n,%20actividades,%20sue\u00f1o\u2026%20Los%20tratamientos%20suelen%20durar%20varios%20d\u00edas%20o%20semanas,%20pero%20si%20dispone%20de%20menos%20tiempo%20puede%20visitar%20a%20un%20doctor%20y%20le%20recetar\u00e1%20los%20mejores%20productos.%20El%20ayurveda%20es%20originario%20del%20Estado%20de%20Kerala,%20por%20lo%20que%20la%20mayor\u00